Project rules and conventions are defined in CLAUDE.md at the project root.
Read that file for full context before making any changes.

## Quick reference
- Stack: React + Vite, monday-sdk-js, @vibe/core
- Deploy: `npm run deploy:build && mapps code:push --client-side -d "build" -i 14083495`
- Never use fetch() against monday APIs — always use monday.api()
- Use MCP to inspect live board column IDs before writing GraphQL
- All UI work in src/App.jsx and child components under src/